column5:
20 pages; revised according to referees' comments; new references;
  two theorems added; simplified proof; conjecture restated; title changed;
  more friendly introduction

v1: 34 pages, expands and supersedes our preprint `Finitely summable
  Fredholm modules for boundary actions of hyperbolic groups', arXiv:1208.0856;
  v2: final version, to appear in Crelle
